{"tid":254490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白鴿當間諜？ 印度官方：疑似中國派來","createTime":"2017-05-23T08:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T09:49:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3049c88e891b347e92fede32160b89be1597c35","tid":254490,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"2017年5月23日<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2076483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2076483&d=2JFlxaPkajhGzn5ZGSFtZC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=86619750\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2076483&h=e13a140c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2076483</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpg2WxCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpg2WxCA.jpg&h=82b50eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度村民捕獲一隻疑似來自中國的鴿子，並懷疑牠是間諜。（圖擷自hindustantimes）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國派出鴿子當間諜？中印邊界的阿魯納恰爾邦（Arunachal Pradesh）村民21日抓到1隻鴿子，發現該鴿子上綁有中文數字標籤，引發當地居民質疑被監視，印度內政部長辛赫（Rajnath Singh）也呼籲民眾提高警覺。<br />\n<br />\n印度日前拒絕參與中國「一帶一路國際合作高峰論壇」，昨天傳出印度砸大錢購買防空導彈，中印關係持續惡化。今天又傳出中國疑似派出鴿子間諜，印度民眾發現鴿子上出現中文數字，讓他們相當緊張。<br />\n<br />\n印度安嬌地區（Anjaw）官員里巴（Mamata Riba）表示，鴿子可能是中國進行監視的一部分，不過他並未談到鴿子上是否有裝相機。另外鴿子的左腿有綁中文數字標籤，當地官員透露，這是當地首次發現疑似間諜鴿子。<br />\n<br />\n不過里巴表示，該鴿子可能用於研究，目前還不能推測，但根據標籤判斷，鴿子應該是研究性質。內政部長辛赫則呼籲，印度邊境地區應對中國「非常警惕」，以免邊界遭到入侵。"},{"pid":"ec3ca87c2edc7f20ec2d26f9827111501194f69b","tid":254490,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"。。。"},{"pid":"2832ad5bb6abb660083a1bdaeefa8cff50d0209f","tid":254490,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"支那真陰險"},{"pid":"3950b89d5f7adb78d5023ead524dffef59604aa4","tid":254490,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"指鹿為馬"},{"pid":"46c849467bd81786aa52b0ca3058e300235ec0c8","tid":254490,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ea602cb1b44e0e124b469639e29344709e5e29","tid":254490,"uid":21480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d161a8eeeefb2054cac6e7bd22a4bfeaabf7f40d","tid":254490,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"幾時拍隻鴿認罪既片"},{"pid":"55beeb0bf26ad341907ca6a40745b96086cfa797","tid":254490,"uid":38909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:03:58.000Z","msg":"因為佢係印度唯一一樣乾淨既野"},{"pid":"6f0c8f84c7f622345591fabffe3a4ce80cc05c81","tid":254490,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"飛鴿傳書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe1ef34e91418373147d411636d0f20a010fba8","tid":254490,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"支那人真係好狗，用生物武器都做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51abc017db492613fc0f8f7ec8589cf342bc3b8d","tid":254490,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets